Circuit Diagram
Connect the TRIG pin of the ultrasonic sensor to pin 12 of the Arduino.
Connect the ECHO pin of the ultrasonic sensor to pin 11 of the Arduino.
Connect the VCC and GND pins of the ultrasonic sensor to 5V and GND of the Arduino.
Connect the servo motor control wire to pin 3 of the Arduino.
Connect the motor driver module to the Arduino:
IN1 to pin 6
IN2 to pin 5
IN3 to pin 10
IN4 to pin 9
Connect the motors to the motor driver module.
Connect the motor driver VCC and GND to the battery pack and Arduino 5V and GND.
